Package abm

package abm
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Agent
    The Agent class is the base class for all objects of this simulation (stars, planets, and meteorites).
    Board
    The Board class represents the simulation area and manages the agents (stars, planets, and meteorites) within it.
    Generator
    The Generator class is responsible for generating the initial set of agents (stars, planets, and meteorites) for the space simulation.
    InteractionManager
    The InteractionManager class handles agent movement, collision detection and out-of-bounds removal within the simulation area.
    Meteorite
    The Meteorite class represents a meteorite agent within the simulation.
    Planet
    The Planet class represents a planet agent in the simulation.
    ResultsPrinter
    The ResultsPrinter class is responsible for saving simulation results to a text file.
    Simulation
    The Simulation class is the main class for the space simulation application.
    Star
    The Star class represents a star agent within the simulation.
